title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 7/12 - Vikings to the Super Bowl?
description: The show begins with some fodder on the NFL and the defending champ Rams, but then PA makes a significant proclamation regarding the Vikings. Jamie Erdahl was announced as the new host of NFL Network's Good Morning Football, and joins in studio to complete the first hour!
